---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service — vectorspace exchange">

  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-gray">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10">Last updated: March 7, 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">1. Acceptance of terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        By accessing or using the VectorSpace Exchange service ("Service"), including the website at vectorspace.exchange and our API, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the Service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">2. Service description</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        VectorSpace Exchange operates a programmatic advertising exchange that matches ads to user intent using vector embeddings and VCG auctions. The Service is provided to publishers (who integrate our API to display ads) and advertisers (who submit ad campaigns for matching).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">3. Accounts</h2>
